host = http://localhost:5145

### Health Check
GET {{host}}/api/health

### ===== SYNC TRANSCRIPTION ( 60s audio) =====

### STT V1  Sync
POST {{host}}/api/transcribe/stt-v1/sync
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary

------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="sample.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

< ./samples/sample.wav
------boundary--

### STT V2  Sync
POST {{host}}/api/transcribe/stt-v2/sync
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary

------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="sample.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

< ./samples/sample.wav
------boundary--

### Chirp  Sync
POST {{host}}/api/transcribe/chirp/sync
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary

------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="sample.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

< ./samples/sample.wav
------boundary--

### Gemini (Vertex AI)  Sync
POST {{host}}/api/transcribe/gemini/sync
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary

------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="sample.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

< ./samples/sample.wav
------boundary--

### ===== BATCH TRANSCRIPTION (long audio, up to 480 min) =====

### STT V1  Batch (uploads to GCS, then LongRunningRecognize)
POST {{host}}/api/transcribe/stt-v1/batch
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary

------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="long_audio.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

< ./samples/long_audio.wav
------boundary--

### STT V2  Batch (uploads to GCS, then BatchRecognize)
POST {{host}}/api/transcribe/stt-v2/batch
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary

------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="long_audio.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

< ./samples/long_audio.wav
------boundary--

### Chirp  Batch
POST {{host}}/api/transcribe/chirp/batch
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary

------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="long_audio.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

< ./samples/long_audio.wav
------boundary--

### ===== COMPARE PROVIDERS =====

### Compare all providers  Sync (short audio)
POST {{host}}/api/transcribe/compare
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary

------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="sample.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

< ./samples/sample.wav
------boundary--

### Compare all providers  Batch (long audio)
POST {{host}}/api/transcribe/compare/batch
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary

------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="long_audio.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

< ./samples/long_audio.wav
------boundary--

#   ws://localhost:5145/ws/transcribe/stt-v1
#   ws://localhost:5145/ws/transcribe/stt-v2
#   ws://localhost:5145/ws/transcribe/chirp
#
# Protocol:
#   Client sends: binary frames (audio PCM 16kHz 16-bit mono, chunks  25KB)
#   Server sends: text frames (JSON StreamingTranscribeResult)

Setup script for GCP authentication and local development.
Configures gcloud CLI, authenticates the user, and sets up
Application Default Credentials (ADC) for the PoC STT GCP project.
Write-Host "  GCP Setup - PoC Speech-to-Text" -ForegroundColor Cyan
Write-Host "  ERROR: gcloud CLI not found." -ForegroundColor Red
Write-Host "[2/4] Authenticating with Google Cloud..." -ForegroundColor Yellow
Write-Host "  A browser window will open. Sign in with your Google account."
Write-Host "[3/4] Setting active project to '$ProjectId'..." -ForegroundColor Yellow
Write-Host "  ERROR: Failed to set project. Do you have access to '$ProjectId'?" -ForegroundColor Red
Write-Host "  OK: Project set to '$ProjectId'." -ForegroundColor Green
Write-Host "[4/4] Setting up Application Default Credentials (ADC)..." -ForegroundColor Yellow
Write-Host "  A browser window will open. Authorize the application."
Write-Host "  ERROR: ADC setup failed." -ForegroundColor Red
